title: Ask Italian
typeOfFood: Lacto, Pizza, Italian, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chain Italian food restaurant. Vegans could find a few things to eat here, including some starters and side dishes such as the rosemary sea salt bread starter, and sorbet for dessert. Chef may make something vegan upon request. Casual, light color decor. Free Wi-Fi.
